    "This is then fed as an input to the TSN feature extractor.",
    "Each video clip thus represents an action example.",
    "We extract the feature from TSN using the AvgPool2d layer while pruning the original average consensus layer.",
    "TSN produces an embedding of size 1024 Â 25 to allow the model to capture the spatio-temporal structure of the RGB video.",
    "The resulting sequence is then fed as input to the fusion model."
